'''Cynthia Narcisi''' (''née'' Cummens) is a freelance artist who has drawn images for ''[[Star Wars]]'', including [[Topps]] trading cards<ref name="2009 Topps SWGS4">{{Topps|set=2009 Topps Star Wars Galaxy Series 4|subset=Artist Sketch Cards|parent=1}}</ref> and the former Learn to Draw feature on [[StarWars.com]].<ref name="Learn to Draw" />

